Hmmm, have you done your newbie armor quests?  I'm not sure if it's better than banded or not.  Check out <A HREF="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/." TARGET="_BLANK">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/.</A>  It has an excellent quest search feature, but it does cost to use it. (I think 9.99 for 3 months, relatively cheap).

Since twinking isn't really an option, you also might want to start thinking of crafted armor quests.  You can talk to the Centaurs in South karana for info on what you'll need to collect to get your armor pieces.  Quests are fun, IMO, anyway.  Gives you something to do and good feeling of accomplishment after you've gotten your piece.

<A HREF="http://steelwarrior.xwarzone.com/" TARGET="_BLANK">http://steelwarrior.xwarzone.com/</A> is a good site, but is down for some reason.

<A HREF="http://steelwarrior.org/" TARGET="_BLANK">http://steelwarrior.org/</A> is the older address, but it still works.

Good luck, warrior. :)

